{
  "version": 2,
  "builds": [
    { "src": "index.html", "use": "@vercel/static" }
  ],
  "routes": [
    { "src": "/(.*)", "dest": "/index.html" }
  ]
}
```

Commit that, and Vercel will auto-redeploy and serve the HTML file correctly.

**Your repo root should look like this when done:**
```
llm-sales-os/
├── index.html        ← the app
├── vercel.json       ← tells Vercel it's static
├── HANDOFF.md
└── PROJECT_STATE.md
